Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:04.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\c&HFFFF&}Face packs...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:08.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\c&HFFFF&}A beauty treatment used by women\Nto stimulate their skin's metabolism,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:12.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\c&HFFFF&}so their faces stay moist and supple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.29,0:00:16.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\c&HFFFF&}But they can also be used in unexpected ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:22.99,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Trace the lines of your hand and you'll find a fuse—\Nthe heart line—to set your deductions alight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.99,0:00:24.54,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Every woman knows face packs freshen your skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:26.74,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But can they transform your mind and body too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:28.30,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:30.00,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:32.59,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:27.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! It's Beika Security!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:29.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:30.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:31.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! We're opening the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:41.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:42.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:45.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.03,0:02:50.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Did I scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:51.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:55.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was putting my face pack on,\Nso I couldn't answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:58.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your security alarm went off...\Ndid something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:00.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:02.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Must've been a glitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:04.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've crossed the infrared sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:16.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so sensitive that this happens once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:17.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, please be sure to lock up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:21.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:38.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, am I full!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:44.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,China has nothing on this place's Chinese cuisine! Don't you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:48.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Actually, ramen's pretty much the same anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:50.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's already this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:54.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s drama show is on tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:57.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! I'm coming home now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:03:58.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:06.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:11.29,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,TM Securities Employee\NTakeo Izumi (25)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:11.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry! I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where you're driving, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:17.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it {\i1}your{\i0} fault for crossing the street without paying attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:18.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:21.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your guys' deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:26.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Megure{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:29.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Police Investigation Section #1?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:32.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Mouri here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:36.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here? Oh, that doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What case are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:42.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! He's involved with a murder case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:47.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.36,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait, Mouri—!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:53.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:05:02.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just crossed paths with the peerless Kogoro Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:06.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I have no idea what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:09.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb! You can spout your excuses when we get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:14.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Would the police call a suspect on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.27,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:30.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:33.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought the suspect, as requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:36.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:39.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:45.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Takeo Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} were a suspect, we obviously wouldn't call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Yeah, I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:54.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,TM Securities, Beika Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:58.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeo Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. You visited this home tonight, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:00.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, no... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:08.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You came at 8:00 exactly, and left at 8:40. Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the exact times...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:12.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know the times so exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:16.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's on the security camera tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:20.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! So he did kill her, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:20.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:28.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left... Yes, at 8:50,\Nthe daughter stopped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:30.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim was still alive then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:35.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, security personnel saw her at 9:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:36.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Security personnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:41.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat snuck into the yard\Nand set off the security alarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:47.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I contacted Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to learn more about the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:47.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the victim, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:58.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikuko Kojima. She managed a chain of discount electronics stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:07:00.17,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Businesswoman\NIkuko Kojima (50)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:00.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was strangled to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:06.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now that everyone is here, let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:07.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:11.26,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Victim's Daughter\NChihiro Kojima (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:11.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the victim's daughter, Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:14.93,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,First to Find Victim\NJuro Yoshioka (48)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:14.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one who found her, Yoshioka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:18.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. According to the security video...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:24.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} arrived at 8:00, and left at 8:40.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:30.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} arrived at 8:50, and left at 9:10.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:34.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Yoshioka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} arrived at 9:20, discovered the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:37.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and called the police at 9:31.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume this is all correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:42.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's on tape, then of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:46.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Her own mother just died! Why is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:51.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it your mother was still alive when you left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:53.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she was!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:56.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or what? Are you suggesting I killed my mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:59.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, nothing of the sort...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:05.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, that puts the time of death between 9:10 and 9:20.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:07.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the house locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:13.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The front door was apparently open\Nwhen Mr. Yoshioka arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:16.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All other doors were locked from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:21.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning the killer was one of these three who used the front door!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:27.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, time-wise, we can probably discount Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:31.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! He has a motive for killing my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:36.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was on the verge of being sued by her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:39.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasted 300 million of her money on a lousy investment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:44.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he's the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:52.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the time of death was between 9:10 and 9:20,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:55.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,time-wise, Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} couldn't have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.58,0:08:56.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:59.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you remember? It was around 9:40...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,9:40...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:04.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:05.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:10.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, he was with us in Beika at 9:40...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:17.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It'd take at least 50 to 60 minutes to get there by car...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:20.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he could've done it somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:22.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The lady has a point!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:29.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Miss. Didn't you have a reason of your own to kill her, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:30.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:32.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:37.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her mother severed all ties with her because of her fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:40.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, her husband is behind bars...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:46.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if that were true,\Nwhy would I need to kill my mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.12,0:09:51.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you asked her for a loan,\Nbut were harshly brushed aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:57.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who argued with her\Nand said you'd kill her someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.79,0:09:59.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:06.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it would appear one of you two is the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:08.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what brought you here tonight, Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:12.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was called here. To be lectured at.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:16.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that made you snap and kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:18.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you get serious, you lousy detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:19.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lousy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:21.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:24.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And what brought you here, Yoshioka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:27.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A work-related meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:33.03,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The circumstances definitely indicate it was one of these two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:47.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the tape. Let me know if you remember or notice anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:54.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} arrives at 8:00 on the dot and goes inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:59.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's at 8:40 exactly that he leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:06.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. The time is 8:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:12.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, 10 minutes later, Ms. Ikuko steps out to speak with the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:17.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So the victim was still alive at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:18.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.86,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What is it? Something seems different...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:26.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At 9:10, Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:34.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, at 9:20, Yoshioka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But as there's no response, he looks inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:41.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...and finds Ms. Ikuko dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:44.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:46.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rewind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:53.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why did you go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:57.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-To contact the police, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:01.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you go outside when there's a phone in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:08.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in shock. So I went to my car to get my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:11.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't blame him; he found a dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:14.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone who ran out shocked,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he did spend 10 minutes in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:19.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do for those 10 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:28.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And look, he's holding something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:36.33,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}"Report — Ozawa Detective Agency"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:43.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So this shows that you embezzled money from the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:47.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be ruined if that were made public!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:48.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I came to talk with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:53.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that discussion ended with you killing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:57.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! She was already dead when I arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like we can really believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:03.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...I thought if this document got out,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:05.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be the prime suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:15.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So then you called the police after hiding it in your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:16.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:20.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can give us your excuses down at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:26.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do it! She really was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:29.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta believe me! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:40.93,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What is it? Something isn't right about this body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}She was dressed for bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:46.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}even though she was expecting visitors...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:47.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's weird, Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:55.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her mouth is wide open, but there aren't any wrinkles at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:05.23,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's it! This was a true death mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Inspector. We're ready to take her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:15.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:19.45,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh no! It'll be too late once the body is taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This body really is weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:24.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:27.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in a bathrobe, and with a face pack on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:29.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing unusual about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:31.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she was going to bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,even though she was expecting company.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:35.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely not how one looks before having company over...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was her daughter coming over...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:43.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yoshioka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was supposed to stop by after Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:46.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was strangled to death, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:50.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0} pointed out that it's weird
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:52.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that her face pack has no wrinkles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:54.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:58.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It should have wrinkles if she was in pain with it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:01.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:02.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:15.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...the culprit applied the face pack after killing the victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:17.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And put her in the bathrobe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:18.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:22.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was dressed like this when you were here, right, Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:24.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:26.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:28.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't the only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:31.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The security guards saw her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:35.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. When I came over due to a false alarm,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was indeed dressed like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:42.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, why would the killer redo her face pack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything seem strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.76,0:15:46.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it was her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her eyes, ears, or lips, for example?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:52.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:54.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her face was covered with the pack and—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:16:00.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised by how her bright purple lips
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:01.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,clashed with her white face.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not wearing lipstick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean like Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s color?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:17.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! So you put the face pack on and met with the guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:24.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Being turned down for the loan caused you to kill your own mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:29.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first slip-up was the malfunctioning security alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was no response,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:34.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the guards would've entered the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.38,0:16:40.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised, you quickly decided to play the role of your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With a face pack and a robe, you could fool them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:47.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are mother and daughter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:52.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But in your rush, you met them with your lipstick still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:57.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you had to remove your mother's lipstick...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:00.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since packs are applied
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:03.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,after washing the face and removing makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:08.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I met the guards and put the face pack on my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:12.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But she was already dead when I got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:15.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows that she and I constantly fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:19.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought everyone would think I killed her, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to believe me! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:27.39,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's no question that she tried to cover things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.39,0:17:30.83,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But it doesn't serve as an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:34.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}All it does is{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10} chan{\r\be10}ge the time of death to be—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:34.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Change?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If the time of death is{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10} chan{\r\be10}ged...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:45.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old man Mouri says...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:51.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:55.62,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's strange. Why hasn't it turned up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:56.46,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:02.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, is it okay for me to leave now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:09.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll need to talk to you again at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:11.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:19.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:21.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! I told you not to hang around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:27.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:33.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:35.33,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:40.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:41.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:52.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we end this play if the main character leaves the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you mean, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.58,0:18:59.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally figured out who really killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you just said that Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:05.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I said nothing of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:10.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I merely exposed her cover-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:14.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Her unnecessary tampering altered the estimated time of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:19.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,which ironically created an alibi for the real killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The real killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:21.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:24.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Surely you're joking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:29.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You vouched that I was in Beika when the murder took place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:33.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if her testimony is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.35,0:19:37.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then the murder took place before 8:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:40.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you could have done it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous! Are you saying you believe her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:48.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And what proof do you have that I killed the woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:52.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Did your mother have poor eyesight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:59.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Y-Yes. But she always wore contacts instead of glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:03.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take another look at the victim's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:05.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe only her left contact is in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.07,0:20:09.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the left one is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:13.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There weren't any contacts in her belongings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:15.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use in looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:17.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the killer has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:25.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The missing contact lens is in your pants cuff, Izumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:30.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:35.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:39.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:42.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a place it could just happen to wind up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:45.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It could only happen to someone with direct contact with the victim—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:50.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the killer, in other words!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.68,0:21:01.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going to sue me for all I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.43,0:21:05.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I only invested how she told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:10.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the minute we lost money, she blamed it all on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:16.02,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Please! Anything but court!\NI'll pay it back, however long it—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:20.05,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I checked the land your parents live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:23.87,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I could postpone things if they sold it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:25.35,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}B-But—!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:28.12,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I already spoke with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:30.38,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}They've agreed to do anything to compensate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:35.29,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Family ties are such a wonderful thing, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.74,0:21:43.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She had to pay...\Nfor dragging my elderly parents into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:11.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work! You saved the day yet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:12.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:16.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The police lost a great man when you left the force!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.54,0:23:18.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.97,0:23:19.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:22.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:24.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Conan! Time to celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:25.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get some food on our way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.97,0:23:27.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More ramen, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:32.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! I'm not talking cheap food here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:33.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Alright!\N- Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:36.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll celebrate with pork ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:43.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured as much...
